      "content": "that's a good start. can u expand on the part about the 'wealthy elite'? i want to make sure i'm not just saying they're rich, but actually explaining why their wealth is fundamentally problematic or illegitimate in the context of racial justice. like, how can i frame it so it's clear that their position is actually an obstacle to progress?",
